name: glycerol-3-phosphate 1-O-acyltransferase
classes: Transferring groups other than aminoacyl groups
comment: Acyl-[acyl-carrier protein] can also act as acyl donor. The enzyme acts only on derivatives of fatty acids of chain length larger than C10.
